snippet.title: Johnny Depp brands ex-wife Amber Heard 'scum' in uncovered 2016 text messages
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp branded his ex-wife Amber Heard as “scum” in text messages sent after their divorce was finalised in 2016, and claimed he “wouldn’t touch” her with a “hazmat suit on”.
#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
